<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Bienvenue chez GlobeGenius ! Votre chasse aux vols à prix réduits commence maintenant</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #333; 
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 0; 
      background-color: #f4f4f4; 
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      background: white; 
      padding: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 30px 20px; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    .logo { 
      max-width: 150px; 
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content { 
      padding: 30px 20px; 
    }
    .welcome-message {
      background: #f0f7ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #4A90E2;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
    }
    .features-list {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .features-list ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .features-list li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .premium-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .premium-section h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2d3436;
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      padding: 15px 30px; 
      background: #e17055; 
      color: white; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 15px 0;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #d63031;
    }
    .testimonials {
      background: #dff0d8;
      border: 1px solid #d6e9c6;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .testimonial {
      font-style: italic;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .testimonial-author {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #27ae60;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      font-size: 12px; 
      color: #999; 
      padding: 20px; 
      background: #ecf0f1;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .emoji {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1><span class="emoji">✈️</span> Bienvenue dans l'aventure GlobeGenius !</h1>
    </div>
    
